snippet.title: POPUCOM Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Pop yourself into an adventure! Become the rainbow!
3D co-op platformer POPUCOM Wishlist Now! 
 
Planned for release on Steam, PlayStation, and Epic Games Store.
Venture with friends in an unknown fantasy world!
Wishlist Now at our official website: https://popucom.hypergryph.global
Twitter：https://twitter.com/popucom_en
Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/popucomEN
